Title: KONG BraidZ Frog Dog Toy, Colors vary
Content: KONG introduces three new characters to our popular BraidZ dog toy line. Made with soft, strong material that has been tightly braided for strength, these Gecko, Frog and Snake shapes maintain BraidZ title as the cutest tug toys on the market. All BraidZ toys are made with minimal stuffing for minimal mess, and the stretchy, tough weave helps floss and clean teeth during play. Each also has a squeaker for added excitement. Available in small, medium and large sizes....
